translation.Message_0_Page_0:
There are three main ranks to climb:
Lieutenant Commander - Leader of a squad
Lieutenant - Deputy to a Lieutenant Commander
Ensign - Soldier in a squad
translation.Message_0_Page_1:
Beyond that are the core members of the Unyielding:
Admiral - Highest rank achieved in the coast guard, like myself.
Captain - Chief of staff
Commander - Right hand of a Captain, like Barlow here
